      • findOne

        public XMLNode findOne(java.lang.String name,
                       boolean recursive)
        Searches for a node with a name 'name' within the children of this node. If recursive is enabled, all the children are searched, otherwise only the immediate children are searched.
        Parameters:
        name - The name to look for
        recursive - If true, search all children, otherwise search immediate children only
        Returns:
        the first occurrence of a node with name 'name' if it exists , null if it's not found
